      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Stop Training for Spreadsheet Management</h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-slate-300">Your estimators should focus on strategy, not troubleshooting broken formulas. See how a custom system can automate your workflow.</p>
      <%= link_to "Talk to us about your estimating workflow", "#contact", class: "btn btn-primary bg-gradient-to-r from-[#4C3F6D] to-[#6d5da1] hover:shadow-purple-200/50 border-none text-white font-bold px-8 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all" %>
