          <div>
            <strong class="text-[#4C3F6D] dark:text-[#8b5cf6]">Material Costing Sync:</strong> <span class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Automatically pull live material prices via API instead of relying on an estimator to check the latest supplier price list.</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#1a1429] rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5">
