          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start p-4 bg-slate-50 dark:bg-[#1a1429] rounded-2xl border border-slate-100 dark:border-white/5">
          <span class="bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-[#4C3F6D] dark:text-[#8b5cf6] p-2 rounded-lg mr-4 mt-1"><i class="fas fa-check text-xs"></i></span>
          <div>
            <strong class="text-[#4C3F6D] dark:text-[#8b5cf6]">Automated Contingency:</strong> <span class="text-slate-900 dark:text-white">Build <strong>Work Breakdown Structures (WBS)</strong> that automatically apply localized risk factors and contingencies.</span>
